From aa930bf8433141dbc244605fe296737b56fa0a73 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nathan Chancellor <nathan@kernel.org>
Date: Mon, 2 Mar 2026 22:33:57 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 01/12] NOTCBL: REPORTED: Revert "Merge branch into tip/master:
 'sched/hrtick'"

This reverts commit c50f05bd3c4e992c1dfb61b14d6f7d999f1381f9, reversing
changes made to 72a2ab46f0458d178712c8cc9546977b4c4e6636.

s390 fails to shutdown properly after this.

Link: https://lore.kernel.org/af549a19-db99-4b16-8511-bf315177a13e@linux.ibm.com/
Signed-off-by: Nathan Chancellor <nathan@kernel.org>
